name: The Golden Temple stills vol 3 "Tender"
description:
Taavi Varm (2020) | 4K (4096x4096) jpg | www.varmstudio.com

This piece is a still-frame render from the video created for the ballet "The Golden Tempel" inspired by a novel of Yukio Mishima and choreography by Teet Kask. Ballet premiered in December 2020 in Estonian National Opera and was nominated for best ballet @ Estonian Theatre Awards.
